<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>系統維護中 - 公益慈善會員系統</title>
<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Arial, "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  
  .maintenance-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    padding: 60px 40px;
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  .icon {
    font-size: 120px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  }
  
  h1 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    color: #667eea;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .message {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  
  .info-box {
    background: #f8f9ff;
    border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin: 30px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .info-box h3 {
    color: #667eea;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  
  .info-box p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }
  
  .status {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #ffc107;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 30px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  
  .footer {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    color: #999;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .maintenance-card {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    
    .icon {
      font-size: 80px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="maintenance-card">
  <div class="icon">🔧</div>
  
  <h1>系統維護中</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">公益慈善會員系統</div>
  
  <div class="status">⏸️ 暫停服務</div>
  
  <div class="message">
    <p>親愛的會員您好，</p>
    <p>系統目前正在進行優化調整，暫時無法提供服務。</p>
    <p>我們正在努力改善，預計很快恢復正常。</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="info-box">
    <h3>🔍 維護原因</h3>
    <p>• 修復 LINE 登入循環問題</p>
    <p>• 優化系統流程</p>
    <p>• 簡化操作邏輯</p>
    <p>• 提升使用體驗</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="info-box">
    <h3>⏰ 預計恢復時間</h3>
    <p>我們正在加緊處理，請稍後再試。</p>
    <p>如有緊急需求，請聯繫客服。</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>感謝您的耐心等待 ❤️</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">
      維護開始時間：2025-10-19
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
// 每 30 秒自动刷新检查是否恢复
setTimeout(() => {
  location.reload();
}, 30000);

console.log('系統維護中，30秒後自動重新檢查');
</script>

</body>
</html>
